item_desc:
The Allegra Drink Mixer is suitable for professional catering use. Easy to use for mixing drinks and making milkshakes. Heavy steel holder provides stability and is easy to clean.

Features
- Commercial-grade 300W motor.
- With 900 ml brushed stainless steel cup Variable control with pulse function
- Deluxe die-cast base and stainless steel spindle
- Stainless steel mixing shaft & double stainless steel blades
- The chrome head
- Safety switch prevents operation without cup in place
- Non-slip rubber feet
- All detachable parts are dishwasher-safe

Specifications:
Control Type On / Off
Product Size 240*215*495 mm
LCD No
Sound Cover Yes (removable)
